config SERVICE_BACKGROUND_AUDIO
    bool "Background audio lifelogging"
    default y if SERVICE_VOICE && SERVICE_AUDIO_ENDPOINT
    depends on SERVICE_VOICE && SERVICE_AUDIO_ENDPOINT && MIC
    help
      Continuous watch microphone streaming to the connected phone over the
      private audio endpoint. Requires voice/Speex and audio endpoint services.
